p and information.</p></ul></td></tr><tr><td><br><img border="0" src="images/references.png" width="282"><br><p align="justify"><b>Method & Webserver : </b><a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/23723246" target="blank">Dehouck Y, Kwasigroch JM, Rooman M, Gilis D. BeAtMuSiC: Prediction of changes in protein-protein binding affinity on mutations. <i>Nucleic Acids Research</i> <b>41</b>:W333-W339 (2013)</a>.<br>doi: <a href="http://dx.doi.org/10.1093/nar/gkt450" target="_blank">10.1093/nar/gkt450</a></p><p align="justify"><b>Participation to the CAPRI experiment : </b><a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/23843247" target="blank">Moretti R. <i>et al.</i> Community-wide evaluation of methods for predicting the effect of mutations on protein-protein interactions. <i>Proteins</i> (2013)</a>.<br>doi: <a href="http://dx.doi.org/10.1002/prot.24356" target="_blank">10.1002/prot.24356</a></p></td></tr></table></td></tr></table><br></body></html>